<section id="Removing_Cloud_Providers" remap="TID_21495">
	<title>Removing Cloud Providers</title>
	<para>
		A cloud provider might require removal from the VMDB if it is no longer in use.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Remove Cloud Providers</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to menu:Clouds[Providers].
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Check the cloud providers to remove.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Configuration)</guibutton>, and then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2157.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Remove Cloud Providers from the VMDB)</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guilabel>OK</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>